ng. Eve maneuvers her way into Margo\'s Broadway role, becomes a sensation and even causes turmoil in the lives of Margo\'s director boyfriend, her playwright and his wife. Only the cynical drama critic sees through Eve, admiring her audacity and perfect pattern of deceit.',12.063080,'/6numIZH6uR3NlJgY9m7nGH0jhs.jpg','1950-11-09',138,'All About Eve',8.0,367.0,'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation'),(707,'English','A View to a Kill','A newly developed microchip designed by Zorin Industries for the British Government that can survive the electromagnetic radiation caused by a nuclear explosion has landed in the hands of the KGB. James Bond must find out how and why. His suspicions soon lead him to big industry leader Max Zorin.',12.840798,'/veDMW7eX6tat86EapsvGEICJ8Tq.jpg','1985-05-24',131,'A View to a Kill',6.0,515.0,'Eon Productions'),(708,'English','The Living Daylights','James Bond helps a Russian General escape into the west. He soon finds out that the KGB wants to kill him for helping the General. A little while later the General is kidnapped from the Secret Service leading 007 to be suspicious.',12.189038,'/yEryMe58dx7zm1QBhQFeuYcv2aH.jpg','1987-06-29',130,'The Living Daylights',6.2,447.0,'United Artists'),(709,'English','Licence to Kill','James Bond and his American colleague Felix Leiter arrest the drug lord Sanchez who succeeds in escaping and takes revenge on Felix and his wife. Bond knows but just one thing: revenge.',11.137888,'/27EySoBH3oBuI6xat2QOquB9X8j.jpg','1989-07-07',133,'Licence to Kill',5.9,549.0,'Eon Productions'),(710,'English','GoldenEye','James Bond must unmask the mysterious head of the Janus Syndicate and prevent the leader from utilizing the GoldenEye weapons system to inflict devastating revenge on Britain.',14.686036,'/5c0ovjT41KnYIHYuF4AWsTe3sKh.jpg','1995-11-16',130,'GoldenEye',6.6,1194.0,'United Artists'),(711,'English','Finding Forrester','Gus van Sant tells the story of a young African American man named Jamal who confronts his talents while living on the streets of the Bronx. He accidentally runs into an old writer named Forrester who discovers his passion for writing. With help from his new mentor Jamal receives a scholarship to a private school.',10.536255,'/heHi6n68fDiQoUc7SMletM9Adjz.jpg','2000-12-21',136,'Finding Forrester',7.0,305.0,'Fountainbridge Films'),(712,'English','Four Weddings and a Funeral','Four Weddings And A Funeral is a British comedy about a British Man named Charles and an American Woman named Carrie who go through numerous weddings before they determine if they are right for one another.',8.990345,'/md9kMKnLG8LG4pMDM98gy5x4K5L.jpg','1994-03-09',117,'Four Weddings and a Funeral',6.6,654.0,'Channel Four Films'),(713,'English','The Piano','After a long voyage from Scotland, pianist Ada McGrath and her young daughter, Flora, are left with all their belongings, including a piano, on a New Zealand beach. Ada, who has been mute since childhood, has been sold into marriage to a local man named Alisdair Stewart. Making little attempt to warm up to Alisdair, Ada soon becomes intrigued by his Maori-friendly acquaintance, George Baines, leading to tense, life-altering conflicts.',7.436758,'/yuGqa81ye11dDAeBZ9MResJSmoY.jpg','1993-05-19',121,'The Piano',7.1,290.0,'New South Wales Film & Television Office'),(714,'English','Tomorrow Never Dies','A deranged media mogul is staging international incidents to pit the world\'s superpowers against each other. Now 007 must take on this evil mastermind in an adrenaline-charged battle to end his reign of terror and prevent global pandemonium.',17.159576,'/k3eI9q7ISgpDEu2CMwR2s6inJVp.jpg','1997-12-11',119,'Tomorrow Never Dies',6.0,941.0,'Eon Productions'),(744,'English','Top Gun','For Lieutenant Pete \'Maverick\' Mitchell and his friend and Co-Pilot Nick \'Goose\' Bradshaw being accepted into an elite training school for fighter pilots is a dream come true.  A tragedy, as well as personal demons, threaten Pete\'s dreams of becoming an Ace pilot.',20.301019,'/orGXnBKfT41LxZhitLkXhqUfJJW.jpg','1986-05-16',110,'Top Gun',6.7,1736.0,'Paramount Pictures'),(745,'English','The Sixth Sense','A psychological thriller about an eight year old boy named Cole Sear who believes he can see into the world of the dead. A child psychologist named Malcolm Crowe comes to Cole to help him deal with his problem, learning that he really can see ghosts of dead people.',18.449169,'/imps263dHNe3SuoaAJORZyNTdDT.jpg','1999-08-06',107,'The Sixth Sense',7.7,3223.0,'Spyglass Entertainment'),(746,'English','The Last Emperor','A dramatic history of Pu Yi, the last of the Emperors of China, from his lofty birth and brief reign in the Forbidden City, the object of worship by half a billion people; through his abdication, his decline and dissolute lifestyle; his exploitation by the invading Japanese, and finally to his obscure existence as just another peasant worker in the People\'s Republic.',11.076971,'/gnKVWiegQ6IoaYA0miR0OdPyI5P.jpg','1987-10-21',163,'The Last Emperor',7.4,362.0,'Columbia Pictures'),(747,'English','Shaun of the Dead','Shaun lives a supremely uneventful life, which revolves around his girlfriend, his mother, and, above all, his local pub. This gentle routine is threatened when the dead return to life and make strenuous attempts to snack on ordinary Londoners.',14.902948,'/ssY4EvRvufUZooNq1buRUrW7lCX.jpg','2004-04-09',99,'Shaun of the Dead',7.5,2479.0,'Universal Pictures'),(752,'English','V for Vendetta','In a world in which Great Britain has become a fascist state, a masked vigilante known only as \'V\' conducts guerrilla warfare against the oppressive British government. When \'V\' rescues a young woman from the secret police, he finds in her an ally with whom he can continue his fight to free the people of Britain.',20.214422,'/AoGpqw4S4ZGgwhlM3FgzFVwyIGl.jpg','2006-03-15',132,'V for Vendetta',7.7,4562.0,'Studio Babelsberg'),(754,'English','Face/Off','An antiterrorism agent goes under the knife to acquire the likeness 