attan\'s subways and sewers, only to confront Jason one final time.',7.743144,'/oAZTwZDHu56IUyq5OQM3q1xX9To.jpg','1989-07-28',100,'Friday the 13th Part VIII: Jason Takes Manhattan',4.8,194.0,'Paramount Pictures'),(10285,'English','Jason Goes to Hell: The Final Friday','Jason Voorhees, the living, breathing essence of evil, is back for one fierce, final fling! Tracked down and blown to bits by a special FBI task force, everyone now assumes that he\'s finally dead. But everybody assumes wrong. Jason has been reborn with the bone-chilling ability to assume the identity of anyone he touches. The terrifying truth is that he could be anywhere, or anybody. In this shocking, blood-soaked finale to Jason\'s carnage-ridden reign of terror, the horrible secret of his unstoppable killing instinct is finally revealed.',9.223325,'/8yLdCrD1Eh6eoGTIIQ4jNBFLkUb.jpg','1993-08-13',87,'Jason Goes to Hell: The Final Friday',4.2,197.0,'New Line Cinema'),(10294,'English','Vacancy','A young married couple becomes stranded at an isolated motel and find hidden video cameras in their room. They realize that unless they escape, they\'ll be the next victims of a snuff film.',7.712309,'/raagPxrhC5098rvMh4QbnlJp7aG.jpg','2007-04-20',80,'Vacancy',6.0,406.0,'Screen Gems'),(10303,'English','The Jewel of the Nile','Joan Wilder is thrust back into a world of murder, chases, foreign intrigue... and love. This time out she\'s duped by a duplicitous Arab dignitary who brings her to the Middle East, ostensibly to write a book about his life. Of course he\'s up to no good, and Joan is just another pawn in his wicked game. But Jack Colton and his sidekick Ralph show up to help our intrepid heroine save the day.',10.571841,'/6VjsIhnIcrz2XdQVHdsMj5DdSa1.jpg','1985-12-04',106,'The Jewel of the Nile',6.0,289.0,'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation'),(10304,'English','Starship Troopers 2: Hero of the Federation','In the sequel to Paul Verhoeven\'s loved/reviled sci-fi film, a group of troopers taking refuge in