o sense that they may have more feelings for each other than they previously thought.',6.449332,'/zxwEJBhSSu5AuKTTd4ugWaCqmg.jpg','2008-09-18',102,'Zack and Miri Make a Porno',6.1,734.0,'Blue Askew'),(10360,'English','Hunger','The story of Bobby Sands, the IRA member who led the 1981 hunger strike in which Republican prisoners tried to win political status. It dramatises events in the Maze prison in the six weeks prior to Sands’ death.',14.322814,'/397BUdT1bIt9tICgq7wSbF05Dsy.jpg','2008-05-15',96,'Hunger',7.2,311.0,'Blast! Films'),(10362,'English','Two Lovers','A depressed man moves back in with his parents following a recent heartbreak.',8.032616,'/3hZTaUN3WYJ9gaOAzWZ6wWlKIGk.jpg','2008-11-19',110,'Two Lovers',6.6,157.0,'2929 Productions'),(10376,'Italian','La leggenda del pianista sull\'oceano','The story of a virtuoso piano player who lives his entire life aboard an ocean liner. Born and raised on the ship, 1900 (Tim Roth) learned about the outside world through interactions with passengers, never setting foot on land, even for the love of his life. Years later, the ship may be destroyed, and a former band member fears that 1900 may still be aboard, willing to go down with the ship.',7.668214,'/wss1PkvHD2cYH6lu5mSa2MgGoi.jpg','1998-10-28',170,'The Legend of 1900',8.1,554.0,'Medusa Film'),(10377,'English','My Cousin Vinny','Two carefree pals traveling through Alabama are mistakenly arrested, and charged with murder. Fortunately, one of them has a cousin who\'s a lawyer - Vincent Gambini, a former auto mechanic from Brooklyn who just passed his bar exam after his sixth try. When he arrives with his leather-clad girlfriend , to try his first case, it\'s a real shock - for him and the Deep South!',7.922216,'/zcd2U5BAP0rYOucfcj8nE4VVVKC.jpg','1992-03-13',120,'My Cousin Vinny',7.3,393.0,'Twentieth Century Fox Film Corporation'),(10380,'English','An American Tail: Fievel Goes West','Some time after the Mousekewitz\'s have settled in America, they find that they are still having problems with the threat of cats. That makes them eager to try another home out in the west, where they are promised that mice and cats live in peace. Unfortunately, the one making this claim is an oily con artist named Cat R. Waul who is intent on his own sinister plan.',8.800701,'/gmqgrnENRE2xO1wtK9kBJZrWLYb.jpg','1991-11-21',75,'An American Tail: Fievel Goes West',6.2,180.0,'Universal Pictures'),(10386,'English','The Iron Giant','In the small town of Rockwell, Maine in October 1957, a giant metal machine befriends a nine-year-old boy and ultimately finds its humanity by unselfishly saving people from their own fears and prejudices.',15.441459,'/rdN6IjV4xlDDhrT8ewkkJfPvp2e.jpg','1999-08-06',86,'The Iron Giant',7.6,1470.0,'Warner Bros. Animation'),(10393,'English','The Replacements','Maverick old-guard coach Jimmy McGinty is hired in the wake of a players\' strike to help the Washington Sentinels advance to the playoffs. But that impossible dream hinges on whether his replacements can hunker down and do the job. So, McGinty dusts off his secret dossier of ex-players who never got a chance (or screwed up the one they were given) and knits together a bad-dream team of guys who just may give the Sentinels their title shot.',13.450661,'/cHI4RgNND66gAcV63V5SoS76tVQ.jpg','2000-08-07',118,'The Replacements',6.2,207.0,'Warner Bros.'),(10395,'English','Wolf','Publisher Will Randall becomes a werewolf and has to fight to keep his job.',14.063845,'/46vYy53pidrxXznVT05Z3r5jgjP.jpg','1994-06-17',125,'Wolf',6.0,221.0,'Columbia Pictures'),(10398,'English','Double Jeopardy','A woman framed for her husband\'s murder suspects he is still alive; as she has already been tried for the crime, she can\'t be re-prosecuted if she finds and kills him.',10.876463,'/9Pl7lqUzU7lxQHYjcmTT6ZvbbDY.jpg','1999-09-24',105,'Double Jeopardy',6.2,282.0,'Paramount Pictures'),(10400,'English','The Hurricane','The story of Rubin \"Hurricane\" Carter, a boxer wrongly imprisoned for murder, and the