0',118,'Train to Busan',7.7,984.0,'NEW'),(397243,'English','The Autopsy of Jane Doe','Father and son coroners receive a mysterious unidentified corpse with no apparent cause of death. As they attempt to examine the beautiful young \"Jane Doe,\" they discover increasingly bizarre clues that hold the key to her terrifying secrets.',31.772396,'/hvQgtEMXzQZDCZkkLFPK6cO1FIy.jpg','2016-12-21',86,'The Autopsy of Jane Doe',6.3,799.0,'IM Global'),(397422,'English','Rough Night','Five best friends from college reunite 10 years later for a wild bachelorette weekend in Miami. Their hard partying takes a hilariously dark turn when they accidentally kill a male stripper. Amidst the craziness of trying to cover it up, they\'re ultimately brought closer together when it matters most.',24.317924,'/i66xbL1C6FEWDm2KoX11DHmP4Rz.jpg','2017-06-15',101,'Rough Night',5.6,336.0,'Sony Pictures Entertainment'),(397837,'English','Before I Fall','Samantha Kingston has everything. Then, everything changes. After one fateful night, she wakes up with no future at all. Trapped into reliving the same day over and over, she begins to question just how perfect her life really was.',38.995136,'/eowzonDJMCuNXoJGVkP9Z7oCmiM.jpg','2017-03-02',98,'Before I Fall',6.8,651.0,'Jon Shestack Productions'),(398929,'French','Alibi.com','Greg founded a company called Alibi.com that creates any type of alibi. With his associate, Augustin, and Medhi his new employee, they devise unstoppable stratagems and stagings to cover their clients. But meeting Flo, a pretty blonde who hates men who lie, will complicate Greg\'s life, which begins by hiding the true nature of his activity. During the presentation to parents, Greg understands that Gérard, the father of Flo, is also one of their clients.',9.095460,'/mC7S1vN4gIE8PR8r0UenMqwXXa7.jpg','2017-02-15',90,'Alibi.com',6.9,389.0,'StudioCanal'),(399019,'English','The Beguiled','During the Civil War, at a Southern girls’ boarding school, young women take in an injured enemy soldier. As they provide refuge and tend to his wounds, the house is taken over with sexual tension and dangerous rivalries, and taboos are broken in an unexpected turn of events.',36.260510,'/yCt9jWUFNpWLSiNpShZr9JFF9oD.jpg','2017-06-23',93,'The Beguiled',5.8,279.0,'American Zoetrope'),(399106,'English','Piper','A mother bird tries to teach her little one how to find food by herself. In the process, she encounters a traumatic experience that she must overcome in order to survive.',11.243161,'/jLRllZsubY8UWpeMyDLVXdRyEWi.jpg','2016-06-16',6,'Piper',8.2,487.0,'Pixar Animation Studios'),(400136,'Japanese','バイオハザード ヴェンデッタ','BSAA Chris Redfield enlists the help of government agent Leon S. Kennedy and Professor Rebecca Chambers from Alexander Institute of Biotechnology to stop a death merchant with a vengeance from spreading a deadly virus in New York.',13.875911,'/88qfHWhlOBYXp69277QFhdPYnWf.jpg','2017-05-27',97,'Resident Evil: Vendetta',6.6,160.0,'Capcom'),(400928,'English','Gifted','Frank, a single man raising his child prodigy niece Mary, is drawn into a custody battle with his mother.',16.025911,'/9Ts7Vc4wLlpI9oox9mkVUE1tBHy.jpg','2017-04-12',101,'Gifted',7.7,549.0,'Fox Searchlight Pictures'),(401104,'English','To the Bone','A young woman dealing with anorexia meets an unconventional doctor who challenges her to face her condition and embrace life.',9.128637,'/rgPysl0uMpxllv43r4udHuRAhn4.jpg','2017-01-22',107,'To the Bone',7.3,714.0,'Mockingbird Pictures'),(402298,'English','Denial','Acclaimed writer and historian Deborah E. Lipstadt must battle for historical truth to prove the Holocaust actually occurred when David Irving, a renowned denier, sues her for libel.',10.754997,'/wyWZZEvual4sIsk6caQ8osMurXc.jpg','2016-09-30',109,'Denial',6.5,161.0,'BBC Films'),(402529,'English','All Eyez on Me','All Eyez on Me chronicles the life and legacy of Tupac Shakur, including his rise to superstardom as a hip-hop artist, actor, poet and activist, as well as his imprisonment and prolific, controversial time at Death Row Records. Against insurmountable odds, Tupac rose to become a cultural icon whose career and persona both continue to grow long after his passing.',9.809168,'/zmgsaKFWbmZ1Grz4SO0PLNxilv3.jpg','2017-06-12',139,'All Eyez on Me',6.3,436.0,'Morgan Creek Productions'),(403119,'English','47 Meters Down','Two sisters on Mexican vacation are trapped in a shark observation cage at the bottom of the ocean, with oxygen running low and great whites circling nearby, they have less than an hour of air left to figure out how to get to the surface.',52.854103,'/2IgdRUTdHyoI3nFORcnnYEKOGIH.jpg','2017-06-15',89,'47 Meters Down',5.1,548.0,'Dimension Films'),(404378,'English','A Street Cat Named Bob','Based on the international best selling book. The true feel good story of how James Bowen, a busker and recovering drug addict, had his life transformed when he met a stray ginger cat.',9.609879,'/6gJ4ENXs2thjxe0mK8TjAZOOPMT.jpg','2016-11-04',103,'A Street Cat Named Bob',7.5,195.0,'Prescience'),(406385,'Italian','Smetto quando voglio: Masterclass','Pietro Zinni is asked by the police to revive the old gang to create a task force that will stop the spread of smart drugs.',5.047357,'/yIAUoB61m4glvZsAduBwqOMfm1V.jpg','2017-02-02',118,'Smetto quando voglio: Masterclass',7.4,158.0,'Fandango'),(406990,'English','What Happened to Monday','In a world where families are limited to one child due to overpopulation, a set of identical septuplets must avoid being put to a long sleep by the government and dangerous infighting while investigating the disappearance of one of their own.',60.581223,'/o6EsOqITcSzcdwD1zxBM9imdxjr.jpg','2017-08-18',123,'What Happened to Monday',7.3,598.0,'Vendome Pictures'),(408220,'English','Justice League Dark','Beings with supernatural powers join together to fight against supernatural villains.',11.279503,'/lGa2sK2LdcHQjasYyukl3P2nras.jpg','2017-01-24',75,'Justice League Dark',7.0,171.0,'Warner Bros. Animation'),(410199,'English','ARQ','Two old friends living in a dystopic future become trapped in a mysterious time loop — one that may have something to do with an ongoing battle between an omnipotent corporation and a ragtag band of rebels.',7.134446,'/39jyxfevRRuLGbh88F5eIzRtOeo.jpg','2016-09-09',88,'ARQ',6.1,340.0,'XYZ Films'),(410718,'English','Before the Flood','A look at how climate change affects our environment and what society can do prevent the demise of endangered species, ecosystems, and native communities across the planet.',5.812786,'/lOu2ETjnndhk89SgqK9lFb3Lb4i.jpg','2016-10-21',93,'Before the Flood',7.9,200.0,'Appian Way'),(411088,'Spanish','Contratiempo','\"The Invisible Guest” turns on a young businessman who wakes up in a hotel room locked from the inside with the dead body of his lover next to him. He hires a prestigious lawyer, and over one night they work together to clarify what happened in a frenetic race against time.',13.906980,'/fptnZJbLzKUHeNlYrAynbyoL5YJ.jpg','2016-12-15',106,'The Invisible Guest',8.1,395.0,'Televisió de Catalunya TV3'),(412105,'English','You Get Me','After arguing with his girlfriend, Ali, Tyler lands in the arms of sexy new girl, Holly. The next morning, he finds that not only does Ali agree to take him back, but Holly is a new student at their school and is dead set on her new man.',12.910289,'/5eV0mIQqSztD3McjO22EOFlQDj1.jpg','2017-06-19',89,'You Get Me',5.5,280.0,'Netflix'),(414190,'English','iBoy','After an accident, Tom wakes from a coma to discover that fragments of his smart phone have been embedded in his head, and worse, that returning to normal teenage life is impossible because he has developed a strange set of super powers.',8.015815,'/hq28FmSpvzG2x2iNm9rsjqUOpbN.jpg','2017-01-27',90,'iBoy',6.0,315.0,'NetFlix'),(416477,'English','The Big Sick','Pakistan-born comedian Kumail Nanjiani and grad student Emily Gardner fall in love but struggle as their cultures clash. When Emily contracts a mysterious illness, Kumail finds himself forced to face her feisty parents, his family\'s expectations, and his true feelings.',23.424794,'/9fJTT8pBxxQsFILJHTtHhdYFr77.jpg','2017-06-23',120,'The Big Sick',7.7,249.0,'FilmNation Entertainment'),(417320,'English','Descendants 2','When the pressure to be royal becomes too much for Mal, she returns to the Isle of the Lost where her archenemy Uma, Ursula\'s daughter, has taken her spot as self-proclaimed queen.',15.842073,'/7TLywOVzWwU1GMyqdjUiSVzBiyc.jpg','2017-07-21',111,'Descendants 2',7.5,171.0,'Walt Disney Television'),(417644,'English','CHiPS','The adventures of two California Highway Patrol motorcycle officers as they make their rounds on the freeways of Los Angeles.',12.238061,'/5HqRLIGVNdet68CEO8N5MVx02i6.jpg','2017-03-23',100,'CHiPS',6.2,277.0,'Warner Bros.'),(417678,'English','Everything, Everything','A teenager who\'s lived a sheltered life because she\'s allergic to everything, falls for the boy who moves in next door.',12.108048,'/c8W3Go48Mw0GoNXsGK4W9hNO4Vf.jpg','2017-05-19',96,'Everything, Everything',7.3,670.0,'Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer (MGM)'),(417870,'English','Girls Trip','Four girlfriends take a trip to New Orleans for an annual festival and, along the way, rediscover their wild sides and strengthen the bonds of sisterhood.',37.964872,'/94nCLn74lBh4pLdZPIad18BpheE.jpg','2017-07-21',122,'Girls Trip',7.1,393.0,'Universal Pictures'),(418078,'English','It Comes at Night','Secure within a desolate home as an unnatural threat terrorizes the world, a man has established a tenuous domestic order with his wife and son, but this will soon be put to test when a desperate young family arrives seeking refuge.',20.504587,'/h9VOirT4dKXzVyVzZZxPfAghmRV.jpg','2017-06-09',91,'It Comes at Night',5.6,357.0,'Animal Kingdom');
